            "recallKnowledgeText": "Recall Knowledge : DC 22",
            "sidebarText": "<h3 class=\"title\">Dread Wraiths</h3>Dread wraiths are much more powerful variants of the standard wraith. A dread wraith is a 9th&#x2011;level creature that can drain the life from creatures via its mere presence. Often, a dread wraith commands a small group of normal wraiths, and in life may have been a bloodthirsty warlord or brutal general.",
